Name: ytTranscript
Description: YouTube transcript tools (easy-to-use wrapper).
Version: 1.0

Overview:
This toolset provides convenient access to YouTube transcripts using the
`youtube-transcript-api` library. You can fetch transcripts by video ID or URL,
list available languages, and translate transcripts when supported.

Commands:
- yt_get_transcript
  Fetch transcript segments for a video.
  Parameters:
  - video_id_or_url (string, required): Video ID or full URL.
  - languages (array, optional): Preferred languages list.
  - proxies (object, optional): Proxy dict.
  - cookies (string, optional): Cookies file path.
  - preserve_formatting (boolean, optional): Preserve formatting.

- yt_get_transcript_text
  Fetch transcript as plain text (joined).
  Parameters:
  - video_id_or_url (string, required)
  - languages (array, optional)
  - proxies (object, optional)
  - cookies (string, optional)
  - preserve_formatting (boolean, optional)

- yt_list_transcripts
  List available transcripts and languages.
  Parameters:
  - video_id_or_url (string, required)
  - proxies (object, optional)
  - cookies (string, optional)

- yt_get_transcript_by_language
  Fetch transcript for a specific language code.
  Parameters:
  - video_id_or_url (string, required)
  - language_code (string, required)
  - proxies (object, optional)
  - cookies (string, optional)
  - preserve_formatting (boolean, optional)

- yt_translate_transcript
  Translate a transcript to a target language.
  Parameters:
  - video_id_or_url (string, required)
  - language_code (string, required): Target language code.
  - source_language_code (string, optional): Source language code.
  - proxies (object, optional)
  - cookies (string, optional)
  - preserve_formatting (boolean, optional)

- yt_get_best_transcript
  One-shot: get the best available transcript as plain text.
  Parameters:
  - video_id_or_url (string, required)
  - languages (array, optional)
  - target_language (string, optional): Auto-translate if needed.
  - proxies (object, optional)
  - cookies (string, optional)
  - preserve_formatting (boolean, optional)

- yt_transcript_range
  Get transcript segments within a time range (seconds).
  Parameters:
  - video_id_or_url (string, required)
  - start (number, required)
  - end (number, required)
  - languages (array, optional)
  - proxies (object, optional)
  - cookies (string, optional)

- yt_transcript_search
  Search transcript text for a keyword.
  Parameters:
  - video_id_or_url (string, required)
  - query (string, required)
  - languages (array, optional)
  - proxies (object, optional)
  - cookies (string, optional)

Usage Examples:
- yt_get_transcript video_id_or_url="dQw4w9WgXcQ" languages=["en"]
- yt_get_transcript_text video_id_or_url="https://youtu.be/dQw4w9WgXcQ"
- yt_list_transcripts video_id_or_url="dQw4w9WgXcQ"
- yt_get_transcript_by_language video_id_or_url="dQw4w9WgXcQ" language_code="es"
- yt_translate_transcript video_id_or_url="dQw4w9WgXcQ" language_code="fr"
- yt_get_best_transcript video_id_or_url="dQw4w9WgXcQ" languages=["en"]
- yt_get_best_transcript video_id_or_url="dQw4w9WgXcQ" target_language="es"
- yt_transcript_range video_id_or_url="dQw4w9WgXcQ" start=30 end=90
- yt_transcript_search video_id_or_url="dQw4w9WgXcQ" query="hello"

Behavior Notes:
- Video ID is extracted automatically from URL formats.
- Translation is only available when the transcript is translatable.

Dependencies:
- youtube-transcript-api
